channel.title: Rocca - Off My Face [Hardcore]
channel.description:
Hey guys! Been a while since I created a track, but here’s another song for the “mdma” album. This one features a jumpy bassline and smooth melodies.
I am thinking about creating a VIP mix with the piano towards the end of the track.
Let us know what ya think!
https://soundcloud.com/roccasounds/off-my-face
